OL,3,CThree held prisoner, blackmailed and
OL,4,Ctortured in town centre lock-up
OL,6,FNine criminals involved in the false
OL,7,Fimprisonment, blackmail and torture of
OL,8,Fthree men at a garage have been
OL,9,Fconvicted in court.
OL,11,FNorthumbria Police said the group
OL,12,Flured their victims to a lock-up off
OL,13,FFowler Street, in South Shields before
OL,14,Fholding them prisoners and subjecting
OL,15,Fthem to "horrifying levels" of
OL,16,Fviolence.
