OL,6,FThe force said they then demanded
OL,7,Fsignificant amounts of money from the
OL,8,Fvictims and their families to secure
OL,9,Ftheir release, following a dispute
OL,10,Fsuspected to be rooted in criminality.
OL,12,FThe three victims were each treated in
OL,13,Fhospital for a range of injuries.
OL,15,FOver the weeks that followed, dawn
OL,16,Fraids were executed across the North
OL,17,FEast with nine suspects arrested and
OL,18,Fcharged with a string of offences.
