OL,6,FDetective Inspector Mark Atherton, the
OL,7,Fsenior investigating officer in the
OL,8,Fcase, said: "This was a terrifying
OL,9,Fordeal for the three victims who were
OL,10,Fsubjected to significant levels of
OL,11,Fviolence.
OL,13,F"While the exact nature of the dispute
OL,14,Fis unknown, it is clear the origins
OL,15,Flie in organised criminal activity and
OL,16,Fthese defendants set about to punish
OL,17,Fand intimidate them that day.
